イヤよ イヤよ イヤよ
見つめちゃイヤー
H O N E Y  F L A S H ╰(•̀ 3 •́)━☆ﾟ.*･｡ﾟ
-----
I wanted to focus on figure drawing this time... Okay, maybe boobs and butts in particular.  

It was a challenge, because a stroke would look good from one angle and then funky from another so you have to work small and slowly build it up.  

I'm hoping there will be some kind of "manipulate" tool in the future so I can push and pull at certain strokes.  

Cutie Honey belongs to Go Nagai.
